Before editing analytics, GTM, GA4, Google Ads, or conversion tracking, read:

- `/ai_context/05_ANALYTICS_GTM_GA4_ADS.md`

Critical rules:

- `purchase` must fire only after confirmed paid order (`order-status` returns `purchase` payload).
- App pushes to `dataLayer` only — no direct `gtag` in app code; GTM forwards to GA4/Ads.
- Do not duplicate GA4 or Google Ads purchase events (one browser `purchase` pipeline).
- Do not wire Measurement Protocol from webhooks without explicit dedupe vs browser `purchase`.
- Funnel events (`add_to_cart`, `begin_checkout`, messenger clicks) are secondary to `purchase`.
- `view_item` should usually be GA4-only in GTM configuration.
